From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: sarun <noreply@sarun>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 19:31:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] find: defer files0 sources through explicit context

Keep -files0-from as an unresolved Find-owned query during argument parsing. Resolve logical stdin or logical-cwd/absolute files only during execution preparation, before output resources are committed. Pure NUL-record decoding preserves order, duplicates, empty input, and Unix path bytes; indexed empty records set failure status without dropping valid neighbors. The actual parser arm also supplies source-operand evidence for ordinary contextual completion without reading the source.

